@startuml e2e-05-prog-tool-calling
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title E2E-05: Programmable Tool Calling Pipeline

participant "QuizOrchestrator\nquiz.py" as QUIZ
participant "ProgToolCalling\nprog_tool_calling.py" as PTC2
participant "PremiumAdapter" as PREM
participant "Sandbox\nsandbox.py" as SB
participant "SessionLog" as LOG

QUIZ -> PTC2 : extract(ptc_result\n  compressed_text="SSDT: maps syscalls...\nCallbacks: PsSetCreateProcess...",\n  raw_tokens=800, compressed_tokens=180)

== Script Generation ==
PTC2 -> PREM : generate(script_prompt +\n  ptc_result.compressed_text)
note right of PREM
  Prompt asks model to write a Python
  script that reads JSON from stdin and
  writes a structured summary to stdout.
end note
PREM --> PTC2 : "import json, sys\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\n..."

== Validation ==
PTC2 -> SB : validate(script)
note right of SB
  RestrictedPython AST check:
  blocks import os, subprocess,
  open(), __class__, etc.
end note

alt validation FAILS
  SB --> PTC2 : ValidationResult(ok=False, reason="Forbidden import: os")
  PTC2 --> QUIZ : ProgToolResult(output_text=ptc_result.compressed_text,\n                script=script, fallback_used=True)
  note right : Falls back to PTCResult — raw KB text\nnever reaches the model even on failure
end

SB --> PTC2 : ValidationResult(ok=True)

== Sandboxed Execution ==
PTC2 -> SB : execute(script, input=ptc_result.compressed_text)
note right of SB
  JobObjectRunner (Windows):
    - RestrictedPython exec
    - Win32 Job Object:
        no child processes,
        memory cap,
        CPU time limit
  DirectRunner (CI/Linux):
    - RestrictedPython exec only
end note

alt execution FAILS or TIMEOUT
  SB --> PTC2 : ExecutionResult(ok=False, output="", error="timeout")
  PTC2 --> QUIZ : ProgToolResult(output_text=ptc_result.compressed_text,\n                script=script, fallback_used=True)
end

SB --> PTC2 : ExecutionResult(ok=True,\n  output='{"summary": "SSDT: syscall table...", "concepts": [...]}')

PTC2 --> QUIZ : ProgToolResult(\n  output_text='{"summary": "SSDT: syscall table...", ...}',\n  script=script,\n  fallback_used=False)

@enduml
